{"tid":1655561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳彥霖升降機 Full version 新疑點","createTime":"2019-10-15T06:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T02:19:24.000Z","uid":127735,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"351dc48a033f4d9255be8010549028904fac2c49","tid":1655561,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:26:10.000Z","msg":"利申：純熟個人推測，無實證<br />\n<br />\n[突發］陳彥霖HKDI升降機Full Version<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655489</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e7w6t5lf8Oc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe7w6t5lf8Oc&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9Go8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=b88184af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e7w6t5lf8Oc</a><br />\n客觀疑點：<br />\nCCTV 秒鐘時間 14 &gt; 16 畫面有定格<br />\nCCTV <span style=\"color: orange;\">中間</span>秒鐘時間 14 &gt; 16 跳左，無出現到 15<br />\nCCTV <span style=\"color: violet;\">大字</span>秒鐘時間 13 &gt; ( 14 &gt; 15 &gt; 16 )，有出現到 15<br />\n<br />\n個人主觀疑點：<br />\n片段中 0:13 ~ 0:22，陳同學係似乎核對緊手上既資料而去睇下係咪簡岩樓層<br />\n片段中 0:43 ~ 0:44，請放慢至 0.25 倍速睇，陳同學左手拎住既好大機會係一部手機，見到有反光面，中間黑色，周邊白色<br />\n片段最後，陳同學出升降機時，小弟睇唔到清楚咩樓層出，但可見升降機門前左邊有圍欄，可以借此推斷樓層<br />\n<br />\n最後就係千其唔好困死自己係一段片到查，其他地方都要查！<br />\n<br />\n【時事台重開】經過一晚，陳彥霖既風向疑點有感<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654939</a>"},{"pid":"2b313ffc1ce0a17ad4ea2149113b63f87cc102a1","tid":1655561,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:26:29.000Z","msg":"十推"},{"pid":"6f3b7fd7f6af57129ba3be61bff3a0b966bbd66f","tid":1655561,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"bee5df9dd982e17b2d321d5ee03817b5ecd4ae73","tid":1655561,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1e43ce0dcd9e91e4b7943136dceb654